{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1544,"text":"To understand the world that live in, we tell stories."},{"time":5513,"text":"And while remixing and sharing have come to define"},{"time":8983,"text":"the web as we know it,"},{"time":10564,"text":"all of us can now be part of that story through simple tools"},{"time":14399,"text":"that allow us to make things online."},{"time":16864,"text":"But video has been left out. It arrived on the web"},{"time":20946,"text":"in a small box, and there it has remained,"},{"time":23692,"text":"completely disconnected from the data and the content"},{"time":26781,"text":"all around it."},{"time":28653,"text":"In fact, in over a decade on the web, the only thing"},{"time":30565,"text":"that has changed about video is the size of the box"},{"time":34161,"text":"and the quality of the picture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37038,"text":"Popcorn changes all of that."},{"time":40206,"text":"It's an online tool that allows anyone to combine video"},{"time":43319,"text":"with content pulled live directly from the web."},{"time":46704,"text":"Videos created with Popcorn behave like the web itself:"},{"time":50239,"text":"dynamic, full of links, and completely remixable,"},{"time":54286,"text":"and finally allowed to break free from the frame."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58585,"text":"I want to give you a demo of a prototype"},{"time":60989,"text":"that we're working on that we'll launch later this fall."},{"time":63029,"text":"It will be completely free, and it will work in any browser."},{"time":67975,"text":"So, every Popcorn production begins with the video,"},{"time":71041,"text":"and so I've made a short, 20-second clip"},{"time":73427,"text":"using a newscaster template that we use in workshops."},{"time":77178,"text":"So let's watch it. We'll go back, and I'll show you how we made it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80862,"text":"Hi, and welcome to my newscast."},{"time":83614,"text":"I've added my location with a Google Map,"},{"time":86055,"text":"and it's live, so try moving it around."},{"time":89423,"text":"You can add pop-ups with live links and custom icons,"},{"time":92815,"text":"or pull in content from any web service, like Flickr,"},{"time":96279,"text":"or add articles and blog posts with links out to the full content."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101109,"text":"So let's go back, and I'll show you what you saw. There was a lot there."},{"time":104748,"text":"So this is the timeline, and if you've ever edited video,"},{"time":108174,"text":"you're familiar with this, but instead of clips in the timeline,"},{"time":111093,"text":"what you're looking at is web events pulled into the video."},{"time":114679,"text":"Now in this Popcorn production we've got"},{"time":117070,"text":"the title card, we've got a Google Map that shows up"},{"time":120823,"text":"picture-in-picture, then Popcorn lets it push"},{"time":123310,"text":"outside the frame and take over the whole screen."},{"time":126670,"text":"There are two pop-ups bringing you some other information,"},{"time":129339,"text":"and a final article with a link out to the original article."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133717,"text":"Let's go to this Google Map, and I'll show you how you can edit it."},{"time":137251,"text":"All you do, go into the timeline, double-click the item,"},{"time":140500,"text":"and I've set it to Toronto, because that's where I'm from."},{"time":142759,"text":"Let's set it to something else."},{"time":146281,"text":"Popcorn immediately goes out onto the web,"},{"time":149412,"text":"talks to Google, grabs the map, and puts it in the display."},{"time":152469,"text":"And it's exactly the same"},{"time":154075,"text":"for the people who watch your production."},{"time":155811,"text":"And it's live. It's not an image. So you click on it,"},{"time":158322,"text":"you zoom in, right down to street view if you want to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162552,"text":"Now in the video, I mentioned adding a live feed,"},{"time":165559,"text":"which we can do right now, so let's add a live feed"},{"time":168740,"text":"from Flickr. Go over to the right-hand side,"},{"time":171624,"text":"grab Flickr from the list of options,"},{"time":174013,"text":"drag it into the timeline,"},{"time":176260,"text":"and put it where you'd like it to go,"},{"time":178734,"text":"and it immediately goes out to Flickr and starts pulling in"},{"time":181197,"text":"images based on the tags. Now, my developers"},{"time":184209,"text":"really like ponies, and so they've set that as the default tag."},{"time":188069,"text":"Let's try something else,"},{"time":191185,"text":"maybe something a bit more relevant to today."},{"time":194753,"text":"Now here are live images being pulled straight from the feed."},{"time":197483,"text":"If you come and watch this a week from now,"},{"time":199071,"text":"this will be completely different,"},{"time":200615,"text":"dynamic, just like the web, and just like the web,"},{"time":203124,"text":"everything is sourced, so click your link,"},{"time":205176,"text":"and you go straight to Flickr and see the source image."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208969,"text":"Everything you've seen today is built with the basic"},{"time":211215,"text":"building blocks of the web: HTML, CSS and JavaScript."},{"time":214775,"text":"That means it's completely remixable. It also means"},{"time":216694,"text":"there's no proprietary software. All you need"},{"time":219258,"text":"is a web browser."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222217,"text":"So imagine if every video that we watched on the web"},{"time":225587,"text":"worked like the web, completely remixable,"},{"time":228633,"text":"linked to its source content, and interactive"},{"time":231380,"text":"for everyone who views it."},{"time":233761,"text":"I think Popcorn could change the way that we tell stories on"},{"time":236757,"text":"the web, and the way we understand the world we live in."},{"time":239135,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}